quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,82,"No e Seytanuuji …óin, …óin …ói no mutana mo, …ói golla golle gaanin …óum. Men laatanike …ói Reenoo…ďe"
  21,83,"[JaŇčto kadi fii] Ayyuuba tuma nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, [O maaki:] \"Min dey memii lam lorra kan, ko An woni ∆Āuroowo Yurmeede yurmtoo…ďe …ďen"
  21,84,"Men jaabinani mo Men hunci ko he…ďi mo kon immorde e lorra, Men Okkiti mo …ďeynguure makko nden e yeru ma…ď…ďe wonndude e ma…ď…ďe kadi, …óum ko Yurmeende immorde ka Amen e waaju wonannde rewoo…ďe …ďen"
  21,85,"[JaŇčto kadi fii] Ismaa'iila e Idriisa e Jalkifli, …ďen fow ko e mun√Ī…ďe …ďen …ďe jeyaa"
  21,86,"Men naadi …ďe e nder Yurmeende Amen nden, pellet, kam…ďe ko …ďe jeyaa…ďe e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen"
  21,87,"[JaŇčto kadi fii] Jannuuni tuma nde o yahunoo ko o tikku…óo o sikki wonnde Men Hattanaake e hoore makko, o noddi ka ni…ďe; \"Wonnde rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa An Senayee wonanii Ma, min dey mi laatike jeyaa…óo e too√Īu…ďe …ďen"
  21,88,"Men jaabinani mo, Men danndi mo immorde e suno ngon, ko wano nii kadi Men danndirta gom…óin…ďe …ďen"
  21,89,"[JaŇčto kadi fii] fii Jakariyaa tuma nde o noddunoo Joomo makko, [o maaki:] Jooma, wata A …óalam bajjo, ko An woni ∆Āur…óo Mo∆ī∆īude ronoo…ďe …ďen"
  21,90,"Men jaabinani mo, Men Okki mo Yahyaa, Men mo∆ī∆īinani mo sonnaajo makko on, pellet, kam…ďe …ďe laatinoke hi…ďe yaccoo e [gollugol] mo∆ī∆īi …óin hi…ďe nodda Men ka rer…óere e kulol …ďe laatinoke yannkinanii…ďe Men"
